    <h2 {...{
      "id": "node-internals"
    }}>{`Node Internals`}</h2>
    <p>{`Two of the most important dependencies of the NodeJS project are `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`V8`}</inlineCode>{` and `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`libuv`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</p>
    <p><inlineCode parentName="p">{`V8`}</inlineCode>{` is an open source JavaScript engine created by Google. The purpose is to execute JavaScript code outside of the browser.`}</p>
