    <p>{`Within the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`src`}</inlineCode>{` directory of the Node project on Github, we can find the JS equivalent `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`.cc`}</inlineCode>{` file for the module `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`node_{module-name}.cc`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</p>
