    <p>{`Within the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`.cc`}</inlineCode>{` files, you'll see a lot of `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`using v8::{name}`}</inlineCode>{` where `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`v8`}</inlineCode>{` allows us to import the C++ definition of JavaScript concepts.`}</p>
