    <p>{`While one thread is processing and waiting for an asynchronous reply, the OS scheduler can schedule another thread for work. This is important for the Nodejs event loop.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "the-nodejs-event-loop"
    }}>{`The Nodejs Event Loop`}</h2>
