    <p>{`When we start up a Node program, Node automatically creates one thread and executes all code on that one thread.`}</p>
    <p>{`The `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`event loop`}</inlineCode>{` itself is like a control structure that tells the one thread what it should be doing at any given time.`}</p>
